style="background: #ddffdd" | {{{1|Yes}}}<noinclude> ---- This template is designed to be used in a table to make a cell with "Yes" in that cell, with a green background.
Example: {|style="font-size: 85%; text-align: center;" class="wikitable" |Example: |{{yes}} |}
== See also == * [[Template:No]] </noinclude>

